sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as YARP Gateway
    participant A as Nocturne API
    participant MW as Middleware Pipeline
    participant S as Service Layer
    participant EF as EF Core
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    C->>G: HTTPS request
    G->>A: HTTP (forwarded headers)
    A->>MW: TenantResolution → Auth → MemberScope
    MW->>A: Routed to Controller
    A->>S: Service method call
    S->>EF: Repository query
    EF->>DB: SQL (with RLS tenant context)
    DB-->>EF: Result set
    EF-->>S: Domain model
    S-->>A: Response DTO
    A-->>G: HTTP response
    G-->>C: HTTPS response
